---
import alertImg from '../../assets/landing/homelab-daily-schedule-herdctl.png';
---

<div class="bg-gray-50 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-16 lg:gap-y-8 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600">Proactive Alerts</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Agents come to you
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
          Agents don't just wait to be checked on. Configure hooks to post results to Discord or Slack after every
          run. Get security findings, build failures, or daily summaries delivered straight to your team's
          channels.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <a
            href="https://edspencer.net/2026/2/22/continuous-security-audit-herdctl"
            class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500"
          >
            Read about continuous security auditing <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/concepts/hooks/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">Hooks &amp; automation docs &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 lg:mt-0">
        <img
          src={alertImg.src}
          alt="Discord notification from a herdctl agent reporting daily security audit findings including critical firewall issues"
          width={alertImg.width}
          height={alertImg.height}
          class="rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-200"
        />
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 italic text-center">
          A homelab agent reports security findings to Discord every morning
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
